The paper deals with image clustering, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also proposes a neural network architecture to solve the problem, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multiple pretrained CNNs as feature extractors also involves multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
